sanity-query.type_post_order_pub:
*[_type == "post"] | order(publishedAt desc) {
    _id,
    title,
    metadata,
    slug,
    publishedAt,
    mainImage,
    categories, 
    createdAt
  }
sanity-query.type_post_slug_curr:
*[_type == "post" && slug.current == $slug][0]{
    _id,
    title,
    metadata,
    body,
    slug,
    publishedAt,
    mainImage,
    author->{
      name,
      image
    },
    categories
  }
sanity-query.type_post_tag_in_t:
*[_type == "post" && $tag in tags]| order(publishedAt desc) {
    _id,
    title,
    metadata,
    slug,
    publishedAt,
    mainImage,
  }
sanity-query.type_propertytype_o:
*[_type == "propertyType"] | order(_createdAt desc) {
    _id,
    name,
    shortDescription,
    longDescription,
    slug,
    imagePrincipale,
    galleryImage[] {
      asset,
      caption
    },
    categories[] {
      value
    },
    modeGestion,
    surface,
    revenuMensuel,
    occupation,
    nbChambres,
    nbSdb,
    coordinates,
    loyer
  }
sanity-query.type_propertytype_s:
*[_type == "propertyType" && slug.current == $slug][0] {
    _id,
    name,
    shortDescription,
    longDescription,
    slug,
    imagePrincipale,
    galleryImage[] {
      asset,
      caption
    },
    categories[] {
      value
    },
    modeGestion,
    surface,
    revenuMensuel,
    occupation,
    nbChambres,
    coordinates,
    loyer
  }
sanity-query.type_faq_order_orde:
*[_type == "faq"] | order(order asc) {
    _id,
    question,
    answer,
    type,
    topic,
    order
  }
sanity-query.type_faq_type_in_t:
*[_type == "faq" && $type in type] | order(order asc) {
    _id,
    question,
    answer,
    type,
    topic,
    order
  }
sanity-query.type_faq_topic:
*[_type == "faq" && topic == $topic] | order(order asc) {
    _id,
    question,
    answer,
    type,
    topic,
    order
  }
sanity-query.type_post_order_pub_1:
*[_type == "post"] | order(publishedAt desc)[$start...$end] {
    _id,
    title,
    metadata,
    slug,
    publishedAt,
    mainImage,
    categories
  }
sanity-query.type_post_reference:
*[_type == "post" && references(*[_type == "categories" && slug.current in $categories]._id)] | order(publishedAt desc)[$start...$end] {
    _id,
    title,
    metadata,
    slug,
    publishedAt,
    mainImage,
    categories
  }
sanity-query.type_post_title_mat:
*[_type == "post" && title match $search] | order(publishedAt desc)[$start...$end] {
    _id,
    title,
    metadata,
    slug,
    publishedAt,
    mainImage,
    "categories": categories[]->{ title, "slug": slug.current },
  }
sanity-query.type_post_reference_1:
*[_type == "post" && references(*[_type == "categories" && slug.current in $categories]._id) && title match $search] | order(publishedAt desc)[$start...$end] {
    _id,
    title,
    metadata,
    slug,
    publishedAt,
    mainImage,
    categories
  }
sanity-query.total_count_type_p_3: { "total": count(*[_type == "post" && references(*[_type == "categories" && slug.current in $categories]._id) && title match $search]) }
